---
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Help - PaintFlow</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
  <nav class="bg-white border-b">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex justify-between h-16 items-center">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">P</div>
          <span class="text-xl font-semibold">PaintFlow</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/login" class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">Sign In</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Help Center</h1>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <a href="#getting-started" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border hover:shadow-md">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">🚀 Getting Started</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Set up your account and send your first estimate</p>
      </a>
      <a href="#estimates" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border hover:shadow-md">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">💰 Estimates</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Create Good/Better/Best pricing</p>
      </a>
      <a href="#scheduling" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border hover:shadow-md">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">📅 Scheduling</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Manage jobs and calendar</p>
      </a>
      <a href="#billing" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border hover:shadow-md">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">💳 Billing</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Stripe, QuickBooks, and payments</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <section id="getting-started" class="bg-white rounded-lg border p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Getting Started</h2>
      
      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">1. Sign up</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Go to <a href="/signup" class="text-blue-600">paintflow.app/signup</a> and enter your email. We'll send you a magic link to sign in — no password needed.</p>
      
      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">2. Complete onboarding</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Set your company name, logo, and default pricing. This takes 2 minutes.</p>
      
      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">3. Create your first estimate</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Click "New Estimate" → Add customer info → Set Good/Better/Best prices → Send via email.</p>
      
      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">4. Get paid</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Connect Stripe from Payments → Stripe. If you do not already have a Stripe account, Stripe hosted onboarding will create one and collect business, owner, and payout details.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="estimates" class="bg-white rounded-lg border p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Estimates</h2>
      
      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Good/Better/Best pricing</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Offer three tiers to increase average job value by 20-30%:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
        <li><strong>Good:</strong> Basic paint, 1 coat, standard prep</li>
        <li><strong>Better:</strong> Premium paint, 2 coats, full prep</li>
        <li><strong>Best:</strong> Premium + extras (caulking, minor repairs)</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">E-signatures</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Customers sign estimates online. No printing or scanning.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="scheduling" class="bg-white rounded-lg border p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Scheduling</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Drag jobs from the unscheduled list to your calendar. Syncs with Google Calendar automatically.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="billing" class="bg-white rounded-lg border p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Billing & Integrations</h2>
      
      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">QuickBooks Sync</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Connect in Settings → Integrations. Customers and invoices sync automatically.</p>
      
      <h3 class="font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Stripe Payments</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Accept credit cards and ACH. 50% deposit collected on estimate acceptance.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Still need help?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Email us at <a href="mailto:support@paintflow.app" class="text-blue-600">support@paintflow.app</a> or check out our <a href="#" class="text-blue-600">video tutorials</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
